title: Allan Quatermain and the Temple of Skulls

sources.description:
Hired to lead an expedition in Africa to find a fabled treasure, an explorer travels through hostile terrain filled with traps and competes with rival fortune hunters. Based on the novel `King Solomon's Mines' by H. Rider Haggard.
2008.  Stars: Sean Cameron Michael, Christopher Adamson, Natalie Stone

metadata.Plot: Allan Quatermain has been recruited to lead an expedition in search of a fabled treasure, deep within Africa. He must avoid hidden dangers.
